# Agent Loop Guidelines

## Overview
- agent_loop.py and the agent_loop/ directory contain functionality for creating agent loops
- AGENT_LOOP_README.md provides documentation for this functionality
- agent_loop_example.py shows example usage

## Usage Guidelines
- Follow the patterns shown in agent_loop_example.py when creating new agent loops
- Refer to AGENT_LOOP_README.md for detailed documentation
- When extending agent loop functionality, maintain compatibility with existing code
- Use the agent loop framework for creating iterative agent workflows

## Best Practices
- Keep agent loop implementations clean and focused
- Document any new agent loop patterns or extensions
- Test agent loops thoroughly before deployment
- Consider performance implications for long-running agent loops
